import cupy as cp
%timeit cp.random.rand(1000,100)
27.2 µs ± 409 ns per loop (mean ± std. dev. of 7 runs, 10,000 loops each)
import numpy as np
%timeit np.random.rand(1000,100)
504 µs ± 1.13 µs per loop (mean ± std. dev. of 7 runs, 1,000 loops each)
import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
address = 'http://url.kr/mjq5wh'
data = np.loadtxt(address)
H_data=data
# 사진찍고 다시해보자
eps =1e-5;c=0.01;H=10.0 #수렴하지 않으면 계속 바꿔가면서 하면 된다.
dH = 0.001
x=H_data[:,0];y=H_data[:,1]
def f(x,H):return (H*x)
def E(x,y,H): return np.sum((y-f(x,H))**2)
Sxy=np.sum(x*y)
Sxx=np.sum(x*x)

# dH = 1
num = 0
while (np.abs(dH) >eps):
    dEdH=(E(x,y,H+dH)-E(x,y,H))/dH
    deltaH=-c*dEdH
    H+=deltaH
    num +=1
    # if num%100 == 0:
    
    print(H)
plt.plot(x,y,"x")
plt.plot(x,H*x)
